feature: users should upload a profile picture up to 2 Mb

    Scenario: user uploads a picture up to 2 Mb 
     Given  user uploads a picture up to 2 Mb 
     Then the upload is done
     
     Scenario: user tries to upload a picture bigger than 2 Mb
      Given user tries to upload a picture bigger than 2 Mb
      Then the upload fails 
      And a message appears about the file's size limit
